title: Gentlemen and Scholars - Thick As Mud (2013)
description:
Thick As Mud, Gentlemen and Scholar's fourth album, became available on March 19th, 2013, and is a perfect blend of blues, rock, and very modern twist. These boys know exactly how to keep listener's on their toes, and Thick As Mud is audible proof.

Recorded, mixed, and mastered in the band's private studio, Thick As Mud serves as an honest interpretation of Gentlemen and Scholars' musical evolution over the past few years.
